---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Mayank, UI/UX Designer" description="About Mayank’s UI/UX design practice and approach.">
  <section class="about-hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">About Mayank</p>
    <h1>I care about the <em>in-between</em> moments—the ones that make a product feel either obvious or overwhelming.</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="about-grid container">
    <div><p class="eyebrow">A little more context</p></div>
    <div class="about-copy">
      <p>I’m a UI/UX designer focused on turning complex problems into experiences that are calm, clear, and useful. I enjoy work where people have something important to do and little patience for software that gets in their way.</p>
      <p>My practice moves between research, product strategy, information architecture, interaction design, and the considered details that bring an interface to life. I work best in close collaboration with the people who know the problem deeply.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="principles container" aria-labelledby="principles-title">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Working principles</p>
        <h2 id="principles-title">How I work</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ol>
      <li><span>01</span><div><h3>Begin with real behaviour</h3><p>Listen to the people doing the work before deciding what needs to change.</p></div></li>
      <li><span>02</span><div><h3>Make the next step visible</h3><p>Good UX does not remove complexity by hiding it. It gives complexity a clear path.</p></div></li>
      <li><span>03</span><div><h3>Design the system, not just the screen</h3><p>Patterns, language, states, and handoffs deserve as much care as a polished interface.</p></div></li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="about-contact container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Get in touch</p>
    <h2>Have a complicated<br />thing to make <em>clearer?</em></h2>
    <a href="mailto:hello@mayank.design">hello@mayank.design <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding-top: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9rem);
  }

  h1, h2, h3 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.055em; line-height: 0.92; }
  h1 { max-width: 13ch; margin: 1rem 0 0; font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8.4vw, 8rem); }
  h1 em { color: var(--accent-deep); }
  .about-contact em { color: var(--accent-deep); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 10vw, 11rem);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about-copy { max-width: 39rem; }
  .about-copy p { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.7rem); letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1.35; }
  .about-copy p + p { margin-top: 1.4em; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  .principles { padding-top: var(--space-6); }
  .principles ol { margin: 0; padding: 0; list-style: none; }
  .principles li { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 5rem 1fr; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .principles li > span { color: var(--accent-deep); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .principles h3 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.7rem); }
  .principles p { max-width: 50ch; margin: 0.65rem 0 0; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  .about-contact { margin-top: var(--space-6); padding: var(--space-5); background: var(--yellow); border-radius: var(--radius-large); }
  .about-contact h2 { margin: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem) 0 0; font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem); }
  .about-contact a { display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }

  @media (max-width: 45rem) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .principles li { grid-template-columns: 2.5rem 1fr; }
  }
</style>
